# tuitube

> A terminal-based video downloader.
> More information: <https://github.com/remorses/tuitube>.

- Start `tuitube`:

`tuitube`

- Switch between options (navigate):

`<Tab>`

- Submit:

`<Enter>`

- Show menu:

`<Ctrl k>`
